"      Stelazine (AE, AR, AU, BB, BF, BH, BJ, BM, BR, BS, BZ, CI, CO, CY, EG, ET, GB, GH, GM, GN, GR, GY, HK, ID, IL, IQ, IR, JM, JO, KE, KW, LB, LR, LY, MA, ML, MR, MU, MW, MX, NE, NG, NL, NZ, OM, PH, PK, PL, QA, SA, SC, SD, SL, SN, SR, SY, TN, TT, TZ, UG, YE, ZM, ZW);",
